description: DeAngelo has been having a very hard time falling asleep lately. Ever since he bumped into the mysterious stranger on the street, it’s all he can think about. As he lies in his bed wide awake and has visions of the incredibly gorgeous Alam Wernik, the visions become reality as these two superstars come together for a wet and wild fuck and suck bathroom session. This is one scene not to be missed.
title: Insomnia
